message.content: ∀ {r : ℝ}, 0 < r → Filter.Tendsto (fun r => Real.Inf {m : ℤ, n : ℤ | abs (r - Real.sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2))}) Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ) (r : ℝ),
  (∀ m n : ℤ, G r = min (abs (r - real.sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2)))) →
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ) (hG : ∀ r, G r = ⨅ (m n : ℤ), |r - Real.sqrt (m^2 + 2 * n^2)|),
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0))

∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ) (hG : ∀ r > 0, G r = Inf {abs (r - Real.sqrt (m ^ 2 + 2 * n ^ 2)) | (m n : ℤ)}),
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
∀ {r : ℝ}, 0 < r → (∃ (m n : ℤ), ∀ ε > 0, ∃ R > r, |r - real.sqrt (m^2 + 2 * n^2)| < ε) → Filter.Tendsto (fun r => infi (fun m n => |r - real.sqrt (m^2 + 2 * n^2)|)) Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ) (hG : ∀ r > 0, ∃ (m n : ℤ), G r = |r - Real.sqrt (m^2 + 2 * n^2)|),
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ) (r : ℝ), (∀ (m n : ℤ), ∃! g, g = |r - real.sqrt (m ^ 2 + 2 * n ^ 2)| → G r = g) → Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
∀ {r : ℝ}, 0 < r → Filter.Tendsto (fun r => infi (fun (m n : ℤ) => |r - Real.sqrt (m^2 + 2 * n^2)|)) Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ) (r : ℝ), (∀ (r > 0), G r = ⨅ (m n : ℤ), |r - Real.sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2)|) → Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ {G : ℝ → ℝ} (h : ∀ r > 0, G r = Inf {abs (r - real.sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2)) | m n : ℤ}),
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
